<number box="[822,885,1841,1867]" pageId="1" pageNumber="22" value="1911.0">1911</number>
, has been considered 
<emphasis box="[1157,1315,1841,1866]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="22">bona species</emphasis>
by 
<bibRefCitation author="Binda" pageId="1" pageNumber="36" refString="Binda, M. G. (1988) Ridescrizione di Macrobiotus echinogenitus Richters, 1904 e sul valore di buona specie di Macrobiotus crenulatus Richters, 1904. Animalia, 15, 201 - 210." type="journal article" year="1988">
